    com.mapbox.services.android.navigation.v5.navigation.NavigationRoute.Builder.addBearing(Double, Double)
    use the bearing paired with NavigationRoute.Builder.origin(Point, Double, Double), NavigationRoute.Builder.destination(Point, Double, Double), or NavigationRoute.Builder.addWaypoint(Point, Double, Double) instead.
    com.mapbox.services.android.navigation.v5.navigation.RouteRefresh.refresh(RouteProgress)
    use RouteRefresh.refresh(RouteProgress, RefreshCallback) instead
